《'''帖木儿古兰经手稿'''》，又称为《'''阿奎云鲁古兰经手稿'''》，属于公元15世纪[[伊朗|伊朗]][[帖木儿帝国|帖木儿帝国]]所《[[古兰经|古兰经]]》本，本书纸料为[[明朝|明朝]]制品。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=A TIMURID OR AQQUYUNLU QUR'AN ON CHINESE PAPER , IRAN, 15TH CENTURY|url=https://www.christies.com/lotfinder/lot_details.aspx?intObjectID=6255702|access-date=2020-08-14|website=www.christies.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001122616/https://www.christies.com/lotfinder/lot_details.aspx?intObjectID=6255702|dead-url=no}}</ref>2020年6月25日，被[[佳士得|佳士得]]拍卖，价钱7016250英鎊。<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-06-30|title=Rare Timurid-era Quran sells for over $8m at UK auction|url=https://www.middleeastmonitor.com/20200630-rare-timurid-era-quran-sells-for-over-8m-at-uk-auction/|access-date=2020-08-14|website=Middle East Monitor|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211105034434/https://www.middleeastmonitor.com/20200630-rare-timurid-era-quran-sells-for-over-8m-at-uk-auction/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|last=Rice|first=Stephennie Mulder and Yael|title=The mystery of the Timurid Qur’an|url=https://www.prospectmagazine.co.uk/arts-and-books/the-mystery-of-the-timurid-quran|access-date=2020-08-14|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210515083407/https://www.prospectmagazine.co.uk/arts-and-books/the-mystery-of-the-timurid-quran|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-06-25|title=异域风情艺术品6月上拍佳士得|url=http://art.ifeng.com/2020/0625/3503207.shtml|access-date=2020-12-16|website=凤凰艺术|language=zh|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123050532/http://art.ifeng.com/2020/0625/3503207.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==描述==
《帖木儿古兰经手稿》含有534页，尺寸为22.6 x 15.5厘米，彩色纸张<!--对开本-->，主要由[[明朝|明代]]制造的染色[[贴金|金斑]]点纸组成。纸中注入了铅白，被描述为具有柔软和丝状的质感。色彩含有粉红、紫、橘、蓝及碧色。页面含有[[山水|山水]]、鸟、植物画图。页面上[[阿拉伯文|阿拉伯文]]为[[誊抄体|誊抄体]]，[[苏拉|苏拉]]及三十段<!--（{{lang-ar|جزء |translit =juzʾ}}）-->标题为[[三一体|三一体]]。<ref name=":0" />

==争议==
有学者谴责手稿的拍卖，认为是破坏手稿历史、文化、精神价值。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Sharp|first=Sarah Rose|date=2020-08-05|title=The Sale of a Rare, Gold-painted Qur’an at Christie’s Raises Questions of Provenance|url=https://hyperallergic.com/575419/timurid-quran-christies-sale/|access-date=2020-08-14|website=Hyperallergic|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220114205010/https://hyperallergic.com/575419/timurid-quran-christies-sale/|dead-url=no}}</ref>另有指责[[佳士得|佳士得]]（Christie）在1980年代之前隐藏其细节，可能有掩盖抢劫和贩运情况。<ref name=":1" />

